---
title: Cal Smart Tex-Mex Beyond Meat® Bowls with Mexican Street Corn Slaw
description: Lightly charred corn adds a lovely, smoky quality to Mexican-inspired slaw on top of a wild rice medley. It's finished with Tex-Mex Beyond Meat® and cooling crema for a flavour-packed meal.
